.\" pomointer(1) - Pomodoro tracker and reporter
.\"
.TH POMOINTER 1 "2026-02-04" "1.0" "Pomodoro Time Tracker"
.SH NAME
pomointer \- Process pomodoro files and generate time reports
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B pomointer
[
.B \-h
]
[
.BI \-a " DATE"
]
[
.BI \-b " DATE"
]
[
.BI \-s " SUBJECTS"
]
[
.BI \-e " FORMAT"
]
.I FILE...
.SH DESCRIPTION
The
.B pomointer
program processes files containing pomodoro session records (time management technique) and generates detailed reports of time invested in different tasks or subjects.
.PP
The program reads files with a specific format (documented in
.BR pomofile (5))
that contain:
.IP \(bu 3
Date definition (optional)
.IP \(bu 3
Pomodoro duration (optional)
.IP \(bu 3
Abbreviation definitions (optional)
.IP \(bu 3
Task list with pomodoro counts
.PP
For each file, the program:
.IP 1. 3
Processes
.B #include
directives (optional)
.IP 2.
Looks for date definition (
.BR DATE
variable) or uses file modification date
.IP 3.
Looks for pomodoro duration (
.BR POMO
variable) or uses 30 minutes as default
.IP 4.
Processes abbreviation definitions
.IP 5.
Processes task lines with pomodoro counts
.IP 6.
Generates formatted report
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B \-h
Display this help message and exit.
.TP
.BI \-a " DD/MM/YYYY"
Filter output to show only data from days AFTER this date (inclusive).
Date must be in DD/MM/YYYY format.
.TP
.BI \-b " DD/MM/YYYY"
Filter output to show only data from days BEFORE this date (inclusive).
Date must be in DD/MM/YYYY format.
.TP
.BI \-s " SUBJECT1,SUBJECT2,...,SUBJECTN"
Filter output to show only the specified subjects.
Subjects must be comma-separated, without spaces.
.TP
.BI \-e " FORMAT"
Specify output format. Currently supports:
.RS
.IP "html" 8
Generate HTML output with tables and CSS styling
.RE
.SH EXAMPLES
.PP
Process a basic file:
.RS
.PP
.B pomointer
.I study.pf
.RE
.PP
Process multiple files:
.RS
.PP
.B pomointer
.I week1.pf week2.pf
.RE
.PP
Filter by date (after May 10, 2024):
.RS
.PP
.B pomointer \-a 10/05/2024
.I *.pf
.RE
.PP
Filter by date range (between May 1 and May 15, 2024):
.RS
.PP
.B pomointer \-a 01/05/2024 \-b 15/05/2024
.I record.pf
.RE
.PP
Filter by specific subjects:
.RS
.PP
.B pomointer \-s "Portuguese,Mathematics"
.I study.pf
.RE
.PP
Generate HTML report:
.RS
.PP
.B pomointer \-e html
.I report.pf
.RS
> report.html
.RE
.RE
